data.text:
WANT TO BECOME AN ELITE-BINGE-WATCHER ?

It's easy now sign up, earn points, collect digital rewards, and gain access to exclusive features!

How do you earn points?

Add a series, marathon, or film to your watch list. (125 points per hour)

Add a series, marathon, or film to your seen list. (500 points per hour)

Upload a meme. (5,000 points)

Save a meme. (250 points)

Get a meme you've uploaded saved. (10 points)

Recommend a series, marathon, film, or meme to someone. (100 points)

Binge-watch with someone. (50 points)

Create a movie marathon. (5,000 points)

Add a movie to a marathon you've created. (10 points)

Get a marathon you've created featured. (25,000 points)
